Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:18.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伴随着结尾即开始的咏叹调
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:22.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高举白旗的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:28.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在逃狱后的欢呼声中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:32.87,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被强行拷上了手铐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:38.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:43.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这定罪的把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:46.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇异的独角戏舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:49.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看着 竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:54.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遗落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:54.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺骗吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:56.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多线并行的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:59.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拨开人群
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:02.40,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼喊着 这是我正义的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:04.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}许下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:07.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得赞美的惊恐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:10.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯独拒绝丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:15.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.17,0:22:17.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}过于艳丽的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:19.96,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}带有偏见的分类
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:22.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信没有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:24.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:26.09,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我们已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:28.09,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人人都爱着绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:31.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会满怀悲伤地离去
